sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as kubectl
    participant APIServer as K8s API Server
    participant CRD as NrvqPolicy CRD
    participant Controller as webhook/controller.go
    participant NorviqAPI as Norviq API

    Operator->>APIServer: apply -f crds/examples/policy-*.yaml
    APIServer->>CRD: persist NrvqPolicy object
    CRD-->>Controller: Add/Update informer event
    Controller->>Controller: buildPolicySyncPayload()
    Controller->>NorviqAPI: POST /api/v1/policies
    NorviqAPI-->>Controller: 2xx created/updated
    Controller-->>APIServer: status/log update
